GPL infection problem of Aria2 code

If you package this project directly as a HarmonyOS application, the entire 
project will be infected by the entry/libs/arm64-v8a/libaria2.so file and 
become a GPLv2 licensed project.

However, if you delete all binaries in entry/libs folder, the rest of
the project can be used as public domain code.

Source code for entry/libs/arm64-v8a/libaria2.so:
    https://github.com/SwimmingTiger/aria2

Original license for entry/libs/arm64-v8a/libaria2.so:
    https://github.com/SwimmingTiger/aria2/blob/1.37.0-ohos/COPYING
